class=title> Where 2 find easy money/exp</span><hr size=1> Hello all. I am lv20 and I have NO pp. ZERO. NON. NADA. NIET.<br>
For some reason I keep spending it as soon as i get it. Fortunately, I have stopped doing that. Now the only problem is getting my fundage back up. I have no idea where to hunt, what quests to do, etc etc. I am currently in France so i am temporarily paralyzed (in the EQ world) but ANY help would be gratly appreciated. The only quest i have found of any use is the Health Potion quest (reward; bone talisman = 200p) And I tried to do the Test. of Vanear quest, only to be backstabbed for 769 by that $£€@¬^ing wandering smuggler that 50+ mob WHY THE £!&amp;^ DID VERANT DROP THAT MOB IN THERE. Anyway I could use some help. I am in LOIO hunting snarks and a (VERY) rare Bloodgill once in a loooong while. Any help would be appreciated GREATLY.<br>
<br>
And now for some troubling things about me;<br>
My base wis is 80.<br>
I have less than 1k of equip on me.<br>
I added STR to this char when i made it.<br>
<br>
Thanks a lot, <br>
Strydir Forestsoul<br>
Druid of 20th Season<br>
Member of The Mystic Rings of Norrath<br>
Drinal Server<br>
<br>
PS I know some people have it worse off, so dont come b€0tch!ng at me about it <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uqueylawindrider.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queyla Windrider</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 11:23:05 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.shipit21st.com/baby.html WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where 2 find easy money/exp</span><hr size=1> Money?<br>
<br>
At 20?<br>
<br>
Ummmmm Unrest?  20 wasn't when I started making money, mobs in loio do drop plat tho.<br>
<br>
Money doesn't really start coming in till about 27, grouped up and the giant fort in FM (or 24ish in WW)<br>
<br>
Q <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uhadiz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>hadiz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/14/01 7:52:47 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where 2 find easy money/exp</span><hr size=1> I'm currently Level 19 hunting in lake of ill omen, and I find the money there to be pretty good. I made about 30pp last night hunting with a Iksar monk partner. We hunted anything that conned blue or yellow to us, I would heal, snare the mob, nuke, whatever the situation called for, and he did all the melee. Also the experience was great. I've gotten 5 of my level 19 spells, which wiped out my bank account entirely, then I traveled to Lake of Ill omen and after just a couple days have about 60pp total. Try to get a partner, and hunt Sarnak Conscripts or Goblin Aggressors/Battlemasters. They drop anywhere from 1-5 gold and the Sarnaks have Words of Tyranny and stuff like that which also sells for a few gold. Or you could always advertise your SoW at the mill for donations. Good luck.<br>
<br>
-Montresor<br>
Druid of the 19th season<br>
Vazaelle <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ustrydir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Strydir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 1:13:30 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Ooh! Ooh! I FOUND A MONEYMAKER</span><hr size=1> Hey hey! I found something that kin make lotsa cash! Do the Bone Talisman Quest! Give a G. Snake Fang, a Tiger Skin, and an Aviak Charm to Errrak Thickshank on Kerra Island gives you a Bone Talisman which sells for 150-300pp!!! I havent tried this yet, but my friend said within a few days he had gone up a level or two and had made 1-2k!!!!<br>
<br>
Strydir <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uwaldin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Waldin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 1:28:37 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ooh! Ooh! I FOUND A MONEYMAKER</span><hr size=1> Oh, and don't do the Testament of Vanear quest to make money. By all means, do it once to get the item for yourself, but the ToV is NO DROP, so you can't make money from selling it.<br>
<br>
At level 20, the best place to make tons of money is to camp the hermit in South Karana together with a partner. In two or three levels you can even solo him. That is the only level 20 mob I know that drops Fine Steel weapons. Not every time, but about 1 in 5 times. Still enough money, and good experience, as the hermit spawns every 5 minutes.<br>
<br>
A more conventional and risk free money making scheme would be to hunt willowisps in West Commons or Eruds Crossing. They won't give xp to you any more, but the Greater Lightstones can be turned in at NK gypsy camp for xp and a book, which you can sell for up to 8 PP to the same vendor. Normal Lightstones sell for 1 PP to a vendor. Unfortunately more than half of the willowisps just have worthless Burned Out Lightstones. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=glyphia>Glyphia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 6:30:19 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Money at 20</span><hr size=1> Dunno if they still sell decently, but..<br>
<br>
Capt Surestout in OOT drops Bracer of Erollisi almost every time. Can sell for 20pp-50pp.<br>
<br>
Just bind by the camp, kill, port to WC, sell, and gate back. If they sell fast, can do this 3-4 times per hour.<br>
<br>
Look around for how to best do the camp. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugwynetwoodsister.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gwynet Woodsister</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 6:34:40 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Money at 20</span><hr size=1> You'll get money while getting exp at your level don't worry.<br>
<br>
One advice though... 80 seems very low for base wisdom. With 100 base wisdom, I can reach 200 wisdom but I lose a lot of AC...<br>
<br>
20 is still pretty low, if I were you I would start over at 90 or if possible 95 base wisdom. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utils.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tils</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 7:03:20 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.datacruz.com/~game/tils.jpg height=184 width=125></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Money at 20</span><hr size=1> If your really desperate go to Thurg and zone into icewell....ask a high level group if you can loot the axes + sheilds if they will..loot em and sell them to the merchants for some pp.....can make a mint from it (ive seen newbies to it on my server)<br>
<br>
