</tr>
</table></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubuzwat.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Buzwat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 10:01:27 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Making Money</span><hr size=1> One has been mentioned that is captian Surestrout but you will die.  He coned yellow a couple times to me at 25 but mostly blue.  Also it is best if you have a druid partner so u can harmony pull he has friends.<br>
The bone quest is only doable if you beg Avo charms in SK as the avos are 28 to 30 lvl.<br>
The best way to make money is the DE guard at the entrance to Lavastorm.  Spawns every 5 minutes and drops a 3pp weapon every time, unlike the stupid hermit.  You will also be making selling SoWs to people running in and out of Lavastorm well donating.<br>
<br>
Cheers<br>
<br>
  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/urumil.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rumil</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/15/01 1:38:04 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.e-corridor.com/images/EQ/tinyrumil.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Making Money</span><hr size=1> a real nice method is to go postal on the Bandits of WK, NK and SK, they are also called raiders btw.<br>
<br>
They drop bronze weapons regularly PLUS they drop Sashes which when handed in Qeynos reward you with more bronze weapons as wel las some coin, faction and mebe even exp. I made a mint doing this at your level. <p>Warden of Tunare<br>
