"Just once or twice its good for your Soul." ~ Oingo Boingo
<br><img src="http://www.ecorridor.com/images/EQ/deathpoketext.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaspreerlinah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>aspreerlinah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/17/01 11:09:11 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Making Money</span><hr size=1> Another place to get pretty good money as well as xp is the ogre island in tim deep. you may want to bring a partner, cause i had a much higher wis at that point.  avoid the main camp... take out the raiders on the rocks they often drop finesteel. aside from that, like the guy said 20 is still pretty low, you may consider a restart with a higher wis. (easy to say  hard to do though)<br>
<br>
Asp <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umarquez7.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Marquez7</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/17/01 5:01:18 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Making Money</span><hr size=1> Hunt gargoyles in OOT...I sold them for about 10pp per eye (98 Cha) and made close to 1500pp from lvl 20-24. After that you can hunt wooly mammoths in Everfrost...I sold tusks for 10+pp to EC vendors and made close to 2000pp from lvl 30-34 (have seen druids in mid twenties hunting them too but I was in LOIO during that time). Good luck. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utandaina.showPublicProfile?language=EN>tandaina</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/18/01 4:24:07 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Making Money</span><hr size=1> Asp would the ogre island be a viable solo spot between 25 and 29?   I'm not sure what the level range on these guys are but on Drinal LoIO is so packed its nearly impossible to find anything to kill... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ustrydir.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Strydir</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(6/29/01 7:03:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Making Money</span><hr size=1> Wow hehe thanks for all the comments whoever made the comment about going to Thurg THANK YOU!!! I made an INSANE amount of cash there! <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td al